{"tid":98814,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"同女友屋企人拜年,冇著NMD俾伯母黑面","createTime":"2017-01-28T16:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T06:53:31.000Z","uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77b88e88581c2ae8e2a7edb838ed1b0097fe1ca1","tid":98814,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"去左女友企樓下飲茶,我當然晨早攞定位於等女友一家黎啦<br />\n<br />\n伯母開頭見到我都笑晒口咁架,點知...<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,伯母=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pizza仔做邊行架?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我做公務員架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(微微笑)政府工好呀,咁你住邊頭架?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我同屋企人住堅尼地城<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(笑晒口)港島區好呀,堅尼地城全部私樓黎架喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係呀...<br />\n<br />\n之後d點心黎到阿伯母即刻夾晒畀我食先,成餐飯有講有笑,食到咁上下我當然識做走出去埋單啦<br />\n<br />\n點知阿伯母望住我對鞋即刻黑晒口面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩,仲著converse呀?咩年代人呀?NMD都冇對,阿女你點識朋友架<br />\n<br />\n原本伯母話叫我上去食下年糕傾下計咁既,點知埋完張單佢之後成家人好似人間蒸發咁,打畀女友whatsapp佢都唔覆,隔左幾個鐘先whatsapp我話伯母要我地分手,叫我唔好再搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882a20bdf3b3fe90968d7e156c0c51c9392ece6c","tid":98814,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"b3c3e971fb5df5639b25b56b272214a0b295f1c9","tid":98814,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"0分"},{"pid":"33b5e91589f54033863a0d03a2ea27966555498e","tid":98814,"uid":18817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:45:56.000Z","msg":"咁死得啦ching 今次好難補鑊 就算你買番對NMD都未必得，因為第一印象好撚重要，而你犯左見家長冇著NMD